    <item>
      <title>02 - Evidence Synthesis and Meta-Analysis</title>
      <link>https://seramirezruiz.github.io/data-science-for-policymaking/material/day-4/2-evidence-synthesis/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://seramirezruiz.github.io/data-science-for-policymaking/material/day-4/2-evidence-synthesis/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;summary&#34;&gt;Summary&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This session introduces participants to narrative reviews, systematic reviews, and meta-analysis. We will explore how to combine evidence from multiple studies and interpret findings from meta-analytic studies, enhancing the ability to draw robust conclusions from existing research.&lt;/p&gt;
