      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;summary&#34;&gt;Summary&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This hands-on workshop focuses on compiling and sorting academic and policy evidence. Participants will learn effective search strategies, methods for evaluating sources, and the use of AI tools for literature mapping, aiming to improve their research efficiency and accuracy.&lt;/p&gt;
